---
title: HelloHero: Honey-Herb Pork Loin & Slaw with Creamy Parsnip-Potato Salad
description: Here comes the much-loved flavour combination of sweet and sour. Take your pork dinner to new levels by coating it in lemon and honey. A creamy potato salad on the side and everyone will be surprised by how irresistible this dish is. Who wants seconds?

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving and under 40g carbohydrates per serving.*

image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/6688a439dea0224ab0733557-218a7a7f.jpeg
